        "start": 1.6,
        "end": 9.121
      },
      {
        "segment": "I think I have always been aware subconsciously of my abilities to master new learnings, but my desire to successfully complete my mission on Earth has been energized by the Orion group into irrational and destructive anger when I fail.",
        "start_offset": 120,
        "end_offset": 356,
        "start": 9.161,
        "end": 30.042
      },
      {
        "segment": "Could you comment on this observation?",
        "start_offset": 357,
