        "end": 31.722
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 398,
        "end_offset": 406,
        "start": 31.742,
        "end": 31.882
      },
      {
        "segment": "We would suggest that as this entity is aware of its position as a Wanderer, it may also consider what pre-incarnative decisions it undertook to make regarding the personal or self-oriented portion of the choosing to be here at this particular time/space.",
        "start_offset": 407,
        "end_offset": 662,
        "start": 34.702,
        "end": 122.108
      },
      {
        "segment": "This entity is aware, as stated, that it has great potential, but potential for what?",
        "start_offset": 663,
        "end_offset": 748,
        "start": 127.248,
        "end": 150.91
      },
      {
        "segment": "This is the pre-incarnative question.",
        "start_offset": 749,
        "end_offset": 786,
        "start": 153.91,
        "end": 162.65
      },
      {
        "segment": "The work of sixth density is to unify wisdom and compassion.",
        "start_offset": 787,
        "end_offset": 847,
        "start": 166.17,
        "end": 185.712
      },
      {
        "segment": "This entity abounds in wisdom.",
        "start_offset": 848,
        "end_offset": 878,
        "start": 190.532,
        "end": 197.232
      },
      {
        "segment": "The compassion it is desirous of balancing has, as its antithesis, lack of compassion.",
        "start_offset": 879,
        "end_offset": 965,
        "start": 200.933,
        "end": 229.114
      },
      {
        "segment": "In the more conscious being this expresses or manifests itself as lack of compassion for self.",
        "start_offset": 966,
        "end_offset": 1060,
        "start": 236.575,
        "end": 260.756
      },
      {
        "segment": "We feel this is the sum of suggested concepts for thought which we may offer at this time without infringement.",
